<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-BR">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Sistema de Gerenciamento de Questões</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0-alpha1/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/5.15.4/css/all.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <img src="https://www.ufc.br/images/_images/a_universidade/identidade_visual/brasao/brasao2_vertical_cor_72dpi.png" alt="Brasão da UFC" class="img-fluid position-absolute" style="top: 80px; left: 30px; width: 200px;" />

    <style>
        body {
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            color: #343a40;
            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
        }

        .header {
            background: linear-gradient(to right, #007bff, #0056b3); 
            color: white;
            padding: 50px 0;
            text-align: center;
        }

            .header h1 {
                font-size: 4rem;
            }

            .header p {
                font-size: 1.2rem;
            }

        .card {
            border-radius: 15px;
            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
        }

            .card:hover {
                transform: scale(1.05);
                box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            }

        .btn-custom {
            background-color: #0056b3;
            color: white;
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
        }

            .btn-custom:hover {
                background-color: #004085; 
            }

        .container {
            padding: 50px 0;
        }

        .img-animation {
            width: 100%;
            height: auto;
            opacity: 0;
            animation: slideIn 2s ease-out forwards;
        }

            .img-animation[data-animation="true"] {
                opacity: 1;
                transform: translateX(0);
            }

        .row {
            animation: fadeInRow 2s ease-out forwards;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <div class="header">
        <h1>Bem-vindo ao Sistema de Questões!</h1>
        <p>Gerencie as questões para crianças do ensino fundamental de forma divertida e dinâmica.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="container">
        <div class="row text-center">
            <div class="col-md-4 d-flex">
                <div class="card shadow-lg p-3 mb-5 bg-white rounded w-100">
                    <img src="https://w7.pngwing.com/pngs/524/374/png-transparent-multicolored-math-illustration-vedic-mathematics-euclidean-children-discuss-math-child-painted-text-thumbnail.png" class="img-animation" alt="Logo Matemática Infantil" data-animation="true">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <h5 class="card-title"></h5>
                        <p class="card-text">Explore questões de matemática e muito mais!</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-4 d-flex">
                <div class="card shadow-lg p-3 mb-5 bg-white rounded w-100">
                    <img src="https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEjEO7xilqAr6N6m4GxrvQDH6n-XrCA26p9OgewhdXQRarrRG6TSjc-UXSipewrrmJpkDa1Zc7BHx3h_2ZoE9DpzCUhjOtStRtehmAnGfzMMejDAYr_Tg45KlIRrhCHvWZxMxOKN3UTN8Thf/s1600/1627912585622617-0.png" class="img-animation" alt="Logo Informática Infantil" data-animation="true">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <h5 class="card-title"></h5>
                        <p class="card-text">Desafios para o aprendizado de Informática</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-4 d-flex">
                <div class="card shadow-lg p-3 mb-5 bg-white rounded w-100">
                    <img src="https://media.licdn.com/dms/image/v2/C5612AQEOW_aOybiE6A/article-cover_image-shrink_600_2000/article-cover_image-shrink_600_2000/0/1520204903899?e=2147483647&v=beta&t=onKTadAgd8HLASp3_fJK310VNuJxA_9uAV7ieCms4xU" class="img-animation" alt="Logo Informática Infantil" data-animation="true">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <h5 class="card-title"></h5>
                        <p class="card-text">Incentive a leitura com questões de algortimos e portugol!</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="text-center mt-5">
        <a class="btn btn-lg btn-custom" asp-controller="Questions" asp-action="Create">Comece Agora</a>
    </div>

    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0-alpha1/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>

    <script>
        document.addEventListener("DOMContentLoaded", function() {
            const images = document.querySelectorAll('.img-animation');
            images.forEach(image => {
                image.setAttribute('data-animation', 'true');
            });
        });
    </script>
</body>
</html>
